Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,=========================================================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,------------------------------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.15,0:00:16.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總是拍不到哥哥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.22,0:00:19.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的戰鬥都有直播吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.25,0:00:23.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以為以桐人的性格 最初開始就會衝出來打呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.53,0:00:27.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不… 別看那傢伙那樣 他其實挺會算計的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.66,0:00:31.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許在等參加人數減少 哪裏躲著呢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.53,0:00:35.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是桐人也不會那麼做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.02,0:00:37.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧 結衣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.26,0:00:41.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 爸爸的話 一定以攝像機都拍不到的速度
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.88,0:00:44.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞬間從敵人的背後偷襲 打倒敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.69,0:00:47.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真說不定呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.32,0:00:50.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且明明是槍的遊戲 卻不用搶 非用劍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.66,0:00:54.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真像哥哥的風格呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.41,0:00:58.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個人好強啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.01,0:01:01.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藍衣服的那個？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.40,0:01:15.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.79,0:01:29.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.19,0:01:34.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定是這次的優勝候補之一吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.84,0:01:38.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 這不是不成嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.42,0:01:41.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒被打倒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.04,0:01:47.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.04,0:01:52.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該是讓對方一定時間內麻痹的攻擊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.39,0:01:57.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像風魔法的「封雷網」一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.99,0:03:55.02,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\pos(640,543)}「死槍」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.99,0:03:55.02,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,489)\blur2\fs35}Death Gun
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.02,0:04:14.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,詩音 開槍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.74,0:04:15.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉？打哪個？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.31,0:04:17.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打那個破披風的！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.55,0:04:18.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了！狙了他！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.13,0:04:19.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.16,0:04:21.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在他開槍之前！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.77,0:04:28.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.49,0:04:35.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.94,0:04:37.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發覺到我的位置了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.12,0:04:38.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.23,0:04:43.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪裏看到過我 被系統判定為可識別了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.78,0:05:30.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才那是…什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.55,0:05:34.59,Extra,NTP,0,0,0,,{\p1\an5\fscx827\fscy375\pos(723,51)}m 0 0 l -10 -6 l -10 -6 l 10 -6 l 10 6 l -10 6 l -10 -6
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.55,0:05:34.59,Extra,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs35\an8\c&H000000&}失去連接
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.73,0:05:47.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和這把槍的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.27,0:05:49.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正名字是死槍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.27,0:05:49.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(743,670)}Death Gun
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.90,0:05:57.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…早晚…也會出現在你們面前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.49,0:06:02.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後…用這把槍…給你們帶去真正的死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.66,0:06:06.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我擁有…這個力量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.00,0:06:08.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.52,0:06:10.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還…沒有結束
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.97,0:06:13.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼…還都…沒有結束
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.11,0:06:17.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's show time
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.19,0:06:23.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在哪裏見過那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.78,0:06:24.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 到底是在哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.53,0:06:27.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對 只可能是那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.14,0:06:29.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在艾恩葛朗特裏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.13,0:06:34.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 你幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.12,0:06:37.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騙…騙人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.41,0:06:39.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙…難道說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.67,0:06:42.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道那傢伙是誰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.58,0:06:45.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…不…之前的名字我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.60,0:06:46.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.06,0:06:51.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙是 「微笑棺木」的成員
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.06,0:06:51.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(666,670)}Laughing Coffin
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.54,0:06:54.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,微笑棺木
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.54,0:06:54.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(640,670)}Laughing Coffin
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.30,0:06:56.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說那傢伙是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.66,0:06:59.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使用菜刀的那個隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.68,0:07:02.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不…不是PoH
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.81,0:07:05.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和PoH的說話方式和態度都完全不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.70,0:07:09.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是剛才的 It's show time
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.81,0:07:11.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是PoH最喜歡的台詞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.38,0:07:14.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是PoH身邊的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.24,0:07:16.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,領導層的幹部玩家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.02,0:07:19.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桐人…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.28,0:07:27.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對沒錯 那傢伙就是死槍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.28,0:07:27.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(832,670)}Death Gun
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.02,0:07:28.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死槍?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.02,0:07:28.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(632,670)}Death Gun
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.32,0:07:34.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是傳聞中 被他射過的玩家再也沒有上線過的那個？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.01,0:07:40.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 他用某種方法將玩家真的殺死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.71,0:07:41.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.07,0:07:45.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現實世界中已經有2個人死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.82,0:08:00.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒現身…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.99,0:08:09.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桐人…你繼續監視橋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.84,0:08:12.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我這就確認那傢伙的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.44,0:08:13.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.46,0:08:28.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.85,0:08:29.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.25,0:08:32.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼短的時間就移動了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.82,0:08:34.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.12,0:08:35.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是個好機會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.25,0:08:37.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,機會？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.11,0:08:40.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個破斗篷沒有顯示在終端上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.89,0:08:43.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你一樣潛到到河裏去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.08,0:08:46.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是這樣的話 他現在的武器應該全部解除掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.84,0:08:51.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿著一把手槍的話應該也能在水裏移動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.36,0:08:54.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便是那樣 只有一把手槍的話我們可以輕鬆的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.87,0:08:55.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.90,0:08:57.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是也看到了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.29,0:09:01.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他用那把黑手槍將Pale Rider殺掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.71,0:09:05.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果被打中 說不定就真的死了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.19,0:09:10.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…不想承認
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.31,0:09:16.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有玩家不是單純的PK而是真的將人殺死這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.52,0:09:17.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但確實存在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.90,0:09:21.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個破斗篷死槍他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.90,0:09:21.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(723,670)}Death Gun
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.55,0:09:25.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我以前經歷的VRMMO中殺了很多人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.55,0:09:25.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我以前經歷的VRMMO中殺了很多人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.86,0:09:29.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明知道對方會死 還是揮動著手中的劍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.44,0:09:33.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.19,0:09:41.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那種傢伙…真的在…GGO…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.97,0:09:53.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,詩音…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.70,0:09:55.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,詩音！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.45,0:10:02.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒事 只是有點被嚇到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.79,0:10:06.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說實話 你所說的我沒辦法馬上相信
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.75,0:10:09.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我也不認為你說的都是胡編亂造出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.93,0:10:12.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝 這就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.67,0:10:16.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之 如果我們不馬上離開這裏的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.95,0:10:23.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以為我們正在交戰的其他玩家會湊過來坐收漁翁之利的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.10,0:10:23.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.00,0:10:26.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我們在此分別吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.17,0:10:28.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有什麼打算啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.72,0:10:30.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去追死槍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.72,0:10:30.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(701,670)}Death Gun
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.27,0:10:33.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,詩音 你盡量不要去靠近他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.89,0:10:34.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.58,0:10:35.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會遵守約定的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.08,0:10:39.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次見到你時我會全力與你一戰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.79,0:10:43.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你沒有攻擊我聽我把話說完
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.54,0:10:47.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.38,0:10:50.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.76,0:10:53.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.93,0:10:57.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也和你一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.28,0:11:01.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死槍那傢伙很強啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.28,0:11:01.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(515,670)}Death Gun
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.76,0:11:04.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你如果輸給他還怎麼和我戰鬥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.90,0:11:05.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.82,0:11:08.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我也不願意 我們還是暫時一起行動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.74,0:11:12.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先把他踢出決賽才對嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.96,0:11:16.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…那傢伙真的很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.22,0:11:22.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們都不知道死槍在哪裏 在不在一起還不是一樣危險
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.22,0:11:22.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(448,670)}Death Gun
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.64,0:11:43.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.08,0:11:46.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來要先解決這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.98,0:11:49.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來進攻 掩護就交給你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.67,0:11:54.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.29,0:12:08.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就現在 詩音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.46,0:12:16.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.53,0:12:39.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死槍應該會沿河北上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.53,0:12:39.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(495,670)}Death Gun
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.69,0:12:42.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在出現下一個犧牲者之前我想阻止他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.42,0:12:44.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,詩音 有沒有什麼好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.47,0:12:51.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算他有什麼神奇的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.08,0:12:53.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從根本上來說是狙擊手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.43,0:12:56.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該很不擅長掩護較少的開闊地帶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.85,0:13:01.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我感覺他應該是要去那座城市的廢墟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.11,0:13:04.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我們也朝著城市前進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.99,0:13:08.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.02,0:13:30.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在SAO 大家都堅守著無論什麼情況也不能讓HP全損
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.91,0:13:34.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為 HP歸零時人就會真的死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.65,0:13:39.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 微笑棺木的人卻殺了數十
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.08,0:13:41.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…是數百人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.60,0:13:44.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最後我們攻略組採取行動
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.84,0:13:49.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,組成討伐隊想要將他們抓獲…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.15,0:13:53.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 我哥哥他…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.36,0:13:56.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他應該也在前線戰鬥了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.21,0:13:59.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很慘烈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.87,0:14:03.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥他從昨晚開始就有點怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.93,0:14:08.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許…他是為了解決以前的宿怨才…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.59,0:14:11.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 不是說打工嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.04,0:14:14.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要先下線了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.91,0:14:18.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想先聯繫一下桐人的委託人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.21,0:14:19.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,委託人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.75,0:14:25.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是讓桐人進入GGO的那個人 肯定會知道些什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.73,0:14:26.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有 小唯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.15,0:14:31.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我不在的這段時間能不能找一下和GGO有關的信息
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.15,0:14:33.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.44,0:14:36.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼各位 請稍等我一陣子了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.75,0:14:57.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒追上死槍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.75,0:14:57.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(701,670)}Death Gun
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.18,0:15:00.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會是我們追過了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.84,0:15:02.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想不會的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.41,0:15:05.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是邊跑邊注意水裏的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.95,0:15:10.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 那麼他現在應該藏在城市的某處吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.04,0:15:12.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,河在這裏就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.82,0:15:18.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK 那就在下次的掃瞄中確定死槍的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.82,0:15:18.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(842,670)}Death Gun
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.45,0:15:20.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在他攻擊其他人之前進行強攻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.04,0:15:22.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣雖然很好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.75,0:15:24.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但有一個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.12,0:15:29.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但不要忘了死槍並不是他真正的用戶名
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.12,0:15:29.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(536,670)}Death Gun
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.38,0:15:31.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也…也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.84,0:15:37.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我記得第一次上場的詩音你不瞭解的有3人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.29,0:15:41.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這中間Pale Rider並不是死槍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.29,0:15:41.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(852,670)}Death Gun
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.32,0:15:42.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是還剩下2人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.11,0:15:46.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,槍士X或是Sterben的其中一人就是他了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.27,0:15:50.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他們兩個都在這裏 我們可沒時間去考慮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.33,0:15:55.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說啊 剛才我突然想到的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.81,0:15:59.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把「槍士」反過來讀就是「死槍」 死槍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.81,0:15:59.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(408,670)}jyuushi
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.81,0:15:59.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(819,670)}shijyuu
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.81,0:15:59.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(957,670)}Death Gun
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.85,0:16:03.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,X是十字架畫十字的手勢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.85,0:16:03.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(553,670)}Cross
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.50,0:16:05.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…這麼想是不是太白癡了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.28,0:16:11.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 不過角色名之類的大家不都那感覺的麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.88,0:16:13.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是從本名上拽字編的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.11,0:16:14.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.61,0:16:16.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.83,0:16:24.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 兩個人都在的話就去槍士X那吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.91,0:16:30.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我和PealRider一樣被麻痹了 你也別慌張進入狙擊狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.16,0:16:30.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.01,0:16:35.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死槍一定會出來 用那把黑色手槍了結我才對
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.01,0:16:35.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(282,670)}Death Gun
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.75,0:16:36.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓那個時機狙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.15,0:16:40.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打的可能是你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.44,0:16:44.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不會那麼狙我這事 我早就明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.91,0:16:46.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓緊吧 沒時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.74,0:16:47.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了哦…夥計
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.83,0:17:00.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和你協力可只有這會哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.88,0:17:15.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桐人 你從北邊開始找
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.24,0:17:24.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.03,0:17:28.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在在這個城市裏的只有槍士X
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.07,0:17:30.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 Sterben不在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.20,0:17:33.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說 槍士X就是死槍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.20,0:17:33.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(828,670)}Death Gun
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.58,0:17:36.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他盯著的大概是這人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.42,0:17:40.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得在莉心進入死槍的射程之前阻止他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.42,0:17:40.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(598,670)}Death Gun
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.32,0:17:42.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 掩護交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.53,0:17:43.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.08,0:18:13.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了 在那
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.01,0:18:17.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看樣子還在等莉心出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.15,0:18:20.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行 現在開始從他背後突襲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.43,0:18:25.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,詩音在運動場前面的大樓裏進入狙擊狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.15,0:18:27.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉？我也一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.63,0:18:31.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為有你的掩護我才能無所畏懼地衝鋒陷陣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.79,0:18:33.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,組合不就是那樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.34,0:18:41.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會在與你分頭30s後開始戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.16,0:18:43.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這點時間夠嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.94,0:18:45.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 足夠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.97,0:18:47.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.68,0:19:09.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要打倒了死槍 那傢伙就會變回敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.68,0:19:09.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(551,670)}Death Gun
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.81,0:19:15.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狙了他 打倒他 然後 忘掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.40,0:19:20.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和那傢伙 一定不會再見面了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.75,0:19:30.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.39,0:19:38.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.95,0:19:42.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死槍應該在運動場內才對
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.95,0:19:42.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(455,670)}Death Gun
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.97,0:20:14.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桐人 你是真的 還是冒牌的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.05,0:20:17.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這下子就能真相大白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.92,0:20:24.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時候 瘋狂廝殺的你的樣子我還記得
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.21,0:20:28.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把這個女人 你的同伴殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.04,0:20:31.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你和那時候一樣發瘋的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.11,0:20:33.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.39,0:20:35.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殺了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.00,0:20:36.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要把我？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.72,0:20:42.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桐人 來吧 讓我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.39,0:20:46.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的憤怒…殺意…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.97,0:20:48.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狂氣的劍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.14,0:20:53.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再讓我看一次
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.50,0:21:12.30,Warning,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs30\fad(450,450)}黑星54式：「54式黑星」仿製蘇聯TT生產的國產槍  因為便宜深受國外痞子喜愛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.03,0:21:12.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑星…54式…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.42,0:21:22.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那把槍…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.05,0:21:26.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼…為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.11,0:21:29.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在…在這裏…出現那把槍…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.46,0:23:39.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集 死亡追擊者
